title: Kyler Murray, Lakers, Jason Whitten, and the Cowboys
itunes:title: Kyler Murray, Lakers, Jason Whitten, and the Cowboys
description:
Colin explains why the measurements of QB Kyler Murray don't help his cause, the best case scenario for the Los Angeles Lakers, TE Jason Witten coming out of retirement, and why this is good news for the Dallas Cowboys. Guests include Chris Haynes, John Lynch, Tom Telesco, Daniel Jeremiah, and Jordan Palmer.
